Romani Calls for Italian Solution for Edison, Corriere Reports

-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 
2011-09-27T08:00:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/romani-calls-for-italian-solution-for-edison-corriere-reports.html
Industry Minister Paolo Romani
wants an Italian solution for the future of power producer
 Edison SpA (EDN)  and may introduce a decree to protect strategic
companies, daily il Corriere della Sera cited him as saying.  The management and the supervisory board of utility A2A SpA
will meet today and tomorrow to discuss the future of Edison,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Vasarri in Rome at 
 cvasarri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  